data.description: Pass through the gates and enjoy the scenery as you arrive at your tranquil paradise. Views from every room! Enter to soaring ceilings with lots of natural light. Entertain friends and family in the large open kitchen as others relax on the patio taking in the sweeping views. In the mornings have your coffee in the sunroom just off your master. 3 minus to the clubhouse, pool and gym. Watch the squad of javelina that go through the yard as well as the deer, foxes, and quail. Live in a rural area that is just 45 minutes to downtown Prescott and Phoenix and an hour to Sedona. Back gate has access to BLM land, which is great for off-roading and  enjoying your toys. Save on utilities with leased solar.
